main event: A witness reported a sighting of an unidentified flying object in Youngstown, Ohio on 12 April 1968.
interesting points: The observation lasted for approximately 5 seconds,The report is part of the Project Blue Book initiative by the U.S. Air Force to document UFO sightings,There is only one confirmed witness for this sighting,Weather conditions were reported as clear during the sighting,The report includes a questionnaire aimed at gathering detailed information about the sighting.
witness description: a 17-year-old male resident from Warren, Ohio
